name: Hobby-programs
body:
### Experience with GitHub
To complete the task, I had to sign up on GitHub, I went to the site and clicked on register, the process was pretty standard. I filled in the details and registered. Immediately after that the guide to using GitHub popped up, I read it and followed the steps to create my first repository. I uploaded the programs i had written in java and completed my task.
